{"tid":1864091,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★ 突發！中國復工遙遙無期 香港棺材存貨只能應付到2月8日","createTime":"2020-02-05T12:19:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T10:00:19.000Z","uid":19454,"like":160,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"6a17df9212e9ddccc8a93e720b626dc82a742d56","tid":1864091,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:19:33.000Z","msg":"香港殯葬業商會指出，已向各殯葬公司發出特別通告，目前香港棺木供應緊張，現在的棺木存貨量估計只能應付到2月8日，因此正與供應商討論相關對策。當地殯葬業者無奈表示，若中國工廠在春節過後不能如期復工，將會造成香港存貨嚴重不足，而開始尋找海外的供應廠商作為出路，因此成本必然上漲，隨後表示「屆時就有機會導致價格上調」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3057670\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3057670&d=SLV77eIUGxkMmCzjf2iSt7Y5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=0b731ff7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3057670&h=00615155\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3057670</a>"},{"pid":"89d24659c2a8e8285bfdc2a98808a649b36c6035","tid":1864091,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:19:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"914fb453e5ce37795c29237290cad4085821dfd7","tid":1864091,"uid":19454,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:20:15.000Z","msg":"瘋搶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=